casebody.data:
RAYONIER, INC., a corporation, et al., v. JANE O. LANG 14 So. (2nd) 569

June Term, 1943

July 16, 1943 En Banc Rehearing Denied September 27, 1943 Marks, Marks, Holt, Gray & Yates, and Harry T. Gray, for appellants. Evan Evans and G. N. Ashmore, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The record in this case having been duly considered and no reversible error appearing, the judgment is affirmed.

*397Affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur. BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., dissent.
